                    </div>
                    <span>This book was an easy reading and I simply find it fascinating. <P>I am thankful to Mr. Harris Kern for giving me the privilage to read this book. I am so thrilled with all the advices and examples given by Ms. Karen Willi.<P>You have NO IDEA what this book has done in My Life especially I was in a situation that I had totally lost my FOCUS & PIRORITY. <P>However, this book has able to rebound my thoughts & decision. <P>I would highly recommend everyone out there to get hold on this book and let its wording enriched your life as it had done mine.<P>Definitely looking forwards to read more NEW books written by Mr. Harris Kern for further enrichment.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">My Intentions were there</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>4</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
                      <span>0</span>
                      /
